Hi Kevin,

That looks fantastic. I did a very similar thing to my
bus, https://picasaweb.google.com/max.bronsema/KKLouiseInteriorRestoration?f
eat=directlink, though you did a superior job. 

I am not sure if yours is a camper. Without my camper interior in the bus
was crazy loud inside. After putting the sound dampener in it was still loud
but noticeably quieter. With the interior back in the bus is even still
quieter. The jalousie windows and my old door seals will be replaced next
and I bet that will help even more. 

You are going to have the quietest bus around, keep up the great work.

Max
